

# Features

- Community aspect like Redit. Auto shows level of person but their language target?

- Input
	* Date, link/title, type (book, article, podcast, video), level (easy, okay, challenging)
	* text only/audio only/text+audio/video+subs
	* Minutes, pages read, speaking minutes

- Words read (start page, finish page, exact if you know it). if not, let the sheet? estimate it from pages or minutes or config to personalized average
